{"tid":443621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我有個痴線flatmate 點算好","createTime":"2017-10-21T17:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T11:11:54.000Z","uid":127740,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b53a7db5fdfdefb8af8885340cd07a1550c6d0","tid":443621,"uid":127740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:06:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟喺外國讀書<br />\n今年我就同三個香港人一齊住<br />\n諗住大家喺外國可以多個照應<br />\n點知其中一個flatmate係痴線嘅<br />\n有一日<br />\n佢沖完涼<br />\n圍住條毛巾續間續間房敲門<br />\n叫我地望住佢<br />\n我問：你做乜尻呀<br />\n佢話：你睇唔到我震波咩？<br />\n之後佢仲要露出一個淫邪嘅笑容<br />\n仲有一次<br />\n朝早六點幾走完火警演習<br />\n完左就一齊返flat啦<br />\nFlatmate A話要去廁所痾尿<br />\n咁我同個痴線flatmate都要去<br />\n佢就爆左一句：不如我地三個一痾吖<br />\n我同flatmate A都嚇到呆撚咗<br />\n之後flatmate A同我講話痴線flatmate試過襯佢沖緊涼嗰時敲佢門同撞佢門<br />\n仲係咁叫俾佢入黎<br />\n之後又突然間喺度尻笑<br />\n我嗰一刻feel到生命受到威脅<br />\n有冇巴絲可教我點做<br />\n利申：勿相認"},{"pid":"3d9d2c9b4ac60118f8db76ac7748b125b06ed446","tid":443621,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:09:41.000Z","msg":"痴線佬出沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無得搬走？"},{"pid":"e33464afe8b89f25e3ef2eaf6aab3afcb0b9d1dd","tid":443621,"uid":84277,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:11:40.000Z","msg":"痴線過佢就無事架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd47bdbb5d337f84b0f7c70f80d52d78a88aac75","tid":443621,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T20:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴線過佢就無事架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"dd5bee633d9ffc8b31f066f4f65b54cfcffb5d61","tid":443621,"uid":34025,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T21:15:40.000Z","msg":"有呢啲痴線佬一齊鳩fing 白痴下先開心"},{"pid":"543a3745bce7d39b9647d1c870ba15c634eb48db","tid":443621,"uid":34295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T21:15:46.000Z","msg":"同你玩下姐"},{"pid":"f3bce925cd5997a851552a70